Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_on_bp_drop_pkt#

RESERVE SPACE UPTO 0x3FFF

RESERVED FOR FORMER IPD_SUB_PKIND_FCS - MOVED TO PIP

RESERVE 4008 - 40FF

IPD_ON_BP_DROP_PKT = IPD On Backpressure Drop Packet

When IPD applies backpressure to a BPID and the corresponding bit in this register is set, then previously received packets will be dropped when processed.
